text: 21 AM / Updated 13 minutes ago BRIEF-Teekay LNG Partners Reports Fourth Quarter Results Reuters Staff Feb 22 (Reuters) - Teekay Lng Partners LP: * TEEKAY LNG PARTNERS REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND ANNUAL 2017 RESULTS * QTRLY ‍VOYAGE REVENUES $126.3 MILLION VERSUS $ 100.8 MILLION ​ * QTRLY GAAP NET INCOME ATTRIBUTABLE TO PARTNERS AND PREFERRED UNITHOLDERS OF $39.9 MILLION​ * ADJUSTED NET INCOME ATTRIBUTABLE TO PARTNERS AND PREFERRED UNITHOLDERS OF $34.0 MILLION IN Q4 OF 2017​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
